    "Furthermore, it is crucial to investigate the robustness of AI-driven security tools.",
    "For example, a robust security tool should ideally predict the repaired program as benign.",
    "However, the existing literature does not definitively address whether a program continues to be predicted as vulnerable even after undergoing a successful repair.",
